# Logs
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
firebase-debug.log*
firebase-debug.*.log*

# Firebase cache
.firebase/

# Firebase config

# Uncomment this if you'd like others to create their own Firebase project.
